name: Inventorybeer gui
tagline: Simple GUI to demonstrate JAVA EE persistence
body:
### Welcome to my GitHub project page

![GUI](http://www.nairaland.com/attachments/4304358_gui_pngc242cab2d90fa07224b0eb48cdddf1ff)This is my first project commit on Github so it might not be Fantastic. I recently decided to go into Java EE and also to host on codes on Github for advice and also for others to learn.

The GUI is to demonstrate Java EE persistence on application client. You can star the project so I will add you as a collaborator or send me an email: nkennannadi@gmail.com.

This project was initially started at[nairaland programming section](http://www.nairaland.com/3356367/learn-java-ee-me/1#49834199) by me.
